Program: Start the Week
Title: Putin's Russia
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b02m2g5c
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 10 Jun 2013
On Start the Week Anne McElvoy talks to the Russian expert Fiona Hill about the many faces of Vladimir Putin, while Vladislav Zubok considers the impact of the past on the Russia of today. Oliver Bullough turns to drink to understand the soul of the nation and the historian Rachel Polonsky considers the cultural landscape of the post-Soviet era. Producer: Katy Hickman. Show less